Service Details: - Provides individualized assessment, counselling and support to women experiencing difficulties with breastfeeding by trained and certified Public Health Nurses and lactation consultants- A Public Health Nurse is available to speak with you during regular business hours- For questions outside of business hours, please call 8-1-1- Individualized services are available by appointment
Dates: - Tue and Fri, by appointment only- Please call the Interior Health Kelowna Health Centre to book your appointment
Eligibility: - After your baby is born, you will be referred by a maternity care nurse - Please call for additional details
